            THOMAS!

211
00:15:03.736 --> 00:15:06.870
    THIS IS FREAKY. MAN.
    RED HASN'T SAID ANYTHING
    ABOUT THE STASH.

212
00:15:06.939 --> 00:15:10.908
WHICH CAN ONLY MEAN HE'S GONE
TO THE MUCH-FEARED STAGE:
BEYOND YELLING.

213
00:15:13.212 --> 00:15:16.047
HE'S GONE DARTH VADER. MAN.

214
00:15:16.115 --> 00:15:19.950
            OR... INSTEAD OF
            RED SNAGGING YOU.

215
00:15:20.019 --> 00:15:22.453
        MAYBE YOU SNAGGED RED...

216
00:15:22.522 --> 00:15:24.455
    DIPPING INTO HYDE'S STASH!

217
00:15:24.524 --> 00:15:26.824
        I'M JUST SAYIN'.
        EVERYONE'S TRYIN' IT.

218
00:15:28.461 --> 00:15:32.396
    I GUESS KELSO'S RIGHT.
    EVERYONE IS TRYING IT.

219
00:15:35.935 --> 00:15:38.970
    I'M TELLIN' YA. THIS STUFF
    ISN'T JUST FOR CAKES.

220
00:15:39.038 --> 00:15:42.006
    IT'S GREAT ALL BY ITSELF.

221
00:15:43.609 --> 00:15:46.511
            [ Chuckling ]
            MMM!

222
00:15:46.579 --> 00:15:49.447
        WAIT. WAIT. WATCH THIS.

223
00:15:57.857 --> 00:16:02.060
    LOOK AT ME.
    I'M WHIPPED-CREAM HEAD!

224
00:16:02.128 --> 00:16:06.531
    FEAR ME!
    ALL FEAR WHIPPED-CREAM HEAD!

225
00:16:06.599 --> 00:16:08.699
        [ Sinister Laughter ]

226
00:16:10.303 --> 00:16:12.303
                MMM!

227
00:16:15.709 --> 00:16:17.942
    KELSO. THAT WAS DELIGHTFUL.

228
00:16:18.010 --> 00:16:23.081
BUT THE ONLY PART YOU LEFT OUT
IS WHERE RED KILLS ME!

229
00:16:24.751 --> 00:16:29.587
        FORMAN. IT WAS MY STASH.
        I DON'T WANNA
        LEAVE YOU HANGIN'.

230
00:16:29.656 --> 00:16:32.390
            BUT I'M GONNA.

231
00:16:32.459 --> 00:16:34.692
            SO GOOD LUCK
            IN MILITARY SCHOOL.

232
00:16:42.635 --> 00:16:46.403
    HOW EXCITING!
    MY FIRST AMERICAN ROAD TRIP.

233
00:16:46.473 --> 00:16:49.073
        I CAN'T WAIT
        TO SEE LAKE DILL-HOLE.

234
00:16:51.110 --> 00:16:53.911
        WELL. THE WAIT IS OVER.
        WE'RE HERE.

235
00:16:53.980 --> 00:16:56.914
        NOW. HOP OUT.
        YOU CRAZY SON OF A GUN.

236
00:17:00.186 --> 00:17:02.587
    THIS IS THE MICHIGAN BORDER.

237
00:17:04.157 --> 00:17:08.225
WELL. WHAT DO YOU KNOW.
    SO WHERE IS LAKE DILL-HOLE?

238
00:17:08.294 --> 00:17:11.996
OH. IT'S RIGHT THERE
BEHIND THE GET BENT MEMORIAL.

239
00:17:13.433 --> 00:17:15.833
SO GET BENT. DILL-HOLE!

240
00:17:15.902 --> 00:17:18.136
        <i> [ Tires Screeching ]</i>

241
00:17:21.307 --> 00:17:24.742
        WHAT'S THE SCORE NOW?
        OH. HERE WE GO.

242
00:17:24.810 --> 00:17:28.513
        FEZ: ONE. THOMAS:
        STRANDED IN MICHIGAN!

243
00:17:30.150 --> 00:17:32.416
                OH. I KILL ME.

244
00:17:32.485 --> 00:17:34.652
NICE JOB.

245
00:17:34.720 --> 00:17:36.887
        THANKS.
        I LEARNED FROM THE BEST.

246
00:17:36.956 --> 00:17:38.889
    THANKS.

247
00:17:38.958 --> 00:17:41.259
I WOULD'VE
TAKEN HIS CLOTHES.

248
00:17:41.327 --> 00:17:43.494
                THAT'S WHY
                YOU'RE THE KING.

249
00:17:45.198 --> 00:17:48.098
    THE GOUDA'S SO GOOD-A.

250
00:17:48.168 --> 00:17:50.401
        THE HAVARTI'S A PARTY!

251
00:17:50.470 --> 00:17:53.237
            HELLO. MILADY.

252
00:17:53.306 --> 00:17:57.775
        "FONDUE" YOU LOVE ME?
                STOP DOING THAT!

253
00:17:57.844 --> 00:18:00.712
            ALL DAY WITH THIS.
            "HEY. 'FONDUE' ME."

254
00:18:00.780 --> 00:18:04.248
            "OOH. I STEPPED
             IN 'FON-DOG-DUE.'"

255
00:18:04.317 --> 00:18:06.550
        OH. MY GOD.
        THIS IS AWFUL.

256
00:18:06.619 --> 00:18:10.621
    MICHAEL. A FEW MINUTES AGO.
    I SMELLED STINKY CHEESE.

257
00:18:10.690 --> 00:18:12.857
        AND IT WAS ME!

258
00:18:15.094 --> 00:18:17.728
    LOOK. I'M SORRY.
    I LOVE YOU.
    BUT I CAN'T DO THIS.

259
00:18:17.797 --> 00:18:21.065
        YOU MEAN.
         YOU CAN'T "FONDUE" IT.

260
00:18:21.134 --> 00:18:24.836
    GOD. WILL YOU SHUT UP!
    LOOK. I AM NOT
    CUT OUT FOR WORK.

261
00:18:24.904 --> 00:18:27.872
I'M CUT OUT FOR HAVING
RICH PEOPLE GIVE ME THINGS.

262
00:18:27.941 --> 00:18:32.176
    BUT YOU GOT A JOB FOR ME.
    I MEAN. DOESN'T THAT
    MAKE YOU SATISFIED?

263
00:18:36.482 --> 00:18:38.415
    OH. MY GOSH!

264
00:18:38.484 --> 00:18:41.185
        IT'S A CHECK!

265
00:18:41.253 --> 00:18:44.221
    AND THAT'S MY NAME!

266
00:18:44.290 --> 00:18:46.224
            MINE!

267
00:18:46.293 --> 00:18:48.126
        SO WE CAN STAY TOGETHER!

268
00:18:48.194 --> 00:18:50.795
    YEAH. AND I CAN
    STILL BE RICH!
                        YEAH!

269
00:18:50.864 --> 00:18:53.264
            WELL. IF THIS ISN'T
            GONNA GO BADLY.
            I'M HEADING HOME.

270
00:18:53.333 --> 00:18:55.867
        NO. WAIT. JACKIE
        DESERVES A CELEBRATION.

271
00:18:55.935 --> 00:18:58.702
        HEY. LET'S GO BUY ME
        THAT REMOTE-CONTROL CAR!

272
00:19:02.108 --> 00:19:07.111
NO. MICHAEL.
MONEY DOESN'T GROW ON TREES.

273
00:19:07.180 --> 00:19:10.214
MONEY<i> DOESN'T</i> GROW ON TREES!

274
00:19:12.852 --> 00:19:15.686
YOU KNOW. I THINK
HAVING A JOB IS CHANGING ME.

275
00:19:15.755 --> 00:19:18.188
    OKAY. THINK ABOUT IT.
    A WHOLE NEW ME.

276
00:19:18.257 --> 00:19:21.592
            [ Together ]
            THAT'D BE GREAT.

277
00:19:25.765 --> 00:19:28.699
                    I GOTTA--
I'M GONNA--
            OKAY. ENOUGH!

278
00:19:28.767 --> 00:19:30.968
            YOU. SIT.

279
00:19:32.438 --> 00:19:36.673
            YOU CAN'T MAKE ME
            JOIN THE ARMY. OKAY?
            I'LL CUT OFF A TOE!

280
00:19:36.742 --> 00:19:40.344
            - WHAT?
            - OKAY. OKAY.

281
00:19:40.413 --> 00:19:43.848
            WE ARE JUST GONNA
            CLEAR THE AIR.

282
00:19:43.917 --> 00:19:45.917
            RIGHT NOW.

283
00:19:48.554 --> 00:19:52.356
                NOW. ERIC.
                THE OTHER NIGHT.

284
00:19:52.425 --> 00:19:54.658
        YOUR FATHER AND I
        WERE GETTING INTIMATE...

285
00:19:54.727 --> 00:19:56.728
    [ Red. Eric Groaning ]

286
00:20:02.402 --> 00:20:06.103
                AND WE REALIZED
                WE DIDN'T HAVE
                ANY PROTECTION.

287
00:20:06.172 --> 00:20:08.673
FOR HUGGING.
WE JUST--

288
00:20:08.741 --> 00:20:11.041
WE HUG.

289
00:20:15.080 --> 00:20:19.283
SO YOUR DAD WENT TO YOUR ROOM
LOOKING FOR ONE OF THOSE
CONDOMS I GAVE YOU...

290
00:20:19.352 --> 00:20:24.422
    AND YOU CAUGHT HIM.
    AND HE HAS JUST BEEN
    SO EMBARRASSED EVER SINCE.

291
00:20:25.858 --> 00:20:28.826
                CONDOMS?

292
00:20:28.895 --> 00:20:32.996
            OH! CONDOMS.

293
00:20:34.300 --> 00:20:38.035
YEAH. CONDOMS.

294
00:20:38.104 --> 00:20:40.037
WHAT DID YOU THINK IT WAS?

295
00:20:46.579 --> 00:20:48.813
    WHAT DID<i> YOU</i> THINK IT WAS?

296
00:20:51.317 --> 00:20:54.118
        [ Together ]
        WHAT DID YOU DO?

297
00:20:54.187 --> 00:20:56.887
            WHAT DID<i> YOU</i> DO?

298
00:21:00.092 --> 00:21:02.793
        I-I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
        OKAY?

299
00:21:02.861 --> 00:21:05.396
            YOU STOLE CONDOMS!
            GET HIM. MOM.

300
00:21:06.432 --> 00:21:08.833
YOU'RE GROUNDED.
                FOR A WEEK.

301
00:21:08.901 --> 00:21:11.535
HYDE TOO.

302
00:21:11.604 --> 00:21:17.107
WHATEVER WAS IN THAT DRAWER
THAT YOU DIDN'T WANT ME TO SEE.
I'M SURE IT WAS HIS.

303
00:21:18.744 --> 00:21:21.612
    FINE. NO COMPLAINTS HERE.
    THANK YOU.

304
00:21:27.253 --> 00:21:31.422
YOU SUPPOSE THERE WAS ACTUALLY
SOMETHING IN THAT DRAWER
HE DIDN'T WANT US TO SEE?

305
00:21:33.326 --> 00:21:35.326
    WHO CARES?

306
00:21:40.233 --> 00:21:43.568
        I KNOW IN ORIENTATION
        WE TALKED ABOUT THEFT
        IN THE WORKPLACE.

307
00:21:43.636 --> 00:21:47.138
    SO I WOULD LIKE TO REPORT
    A THEFT FROM MY CHECK.

308
00:21:47.206 --> 00:21:49.406
            NOW. I DON'T KNOW
            WHO FICA IS.

309
00:21:49.475 --> 00:21:52.876
        BUT THAT BITCH STOLE.
        LIKE. 10% OF MY MONEY.

310
00:21:52.945 --> 00:21:56.414
        ALSO. NOW. I DON'T KNOW
        IF YOU HAVE THIS KEY
        IN YOUR TYPEWRITER.

311
00:21:56.482 --> 00:22:00.150
    BUT WHEN I WRITE "JACKIE."
    I LIKE TO DOT MY "I"
    WITH A SMILEY FACE.

312
00:22:00.219 --> 00:22:03.820
    ALSO. NOW. I PUT THIS
    IN THE SUGGESTION BOX. BUT--

313
00:22:03.889 --> 00:22:06.990
        YOU HAVE SOMETHING
        HANGING FROM YOUR NOSE.

314
00:22:07.059 --> 00:22:10.193
    OH. AND I WANT SATURDAY OFF.
    THANK YOU. BYE.

314
00:22:11.305 --> 00:23:11.292
